{pp}
I have decided to have a look around to see what games are going to be available for our miggy in the next few months
{pp}
The first game news came a few weeks ago when I found out that a game we all thought had been cancelled is still alive and kicking.{p}
I am talking about Maing & Mangle, a wartime simulator which, apparently, should be one of the best of its kind on Amiga.{p}
There are many wargames  available on the Amiga but Main & Mangle belongs to the category of the RTS (Real Time Strategy) games and comes with many features such us real 3D terrain, multiplayer games via TCP/IP and night-time combat.{p}
I don't know much about it but keep and eye on the website for the latest development, news and screenshots.{p}
